title: 206: Rookie Running Backs, College Football Picks
itunes:title: 206: Rookie Running Backs, College Football Picks
description:
Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks break down the impressive rookie running backs across the league and preview their Week 2 matchups. The guys also hit the panic button on a few 0-1 teams before they make their college football picks.
